metadata.name: The Tiger Spirit
metadata.description:
Celebrating all of us who is the cat with tiger spirit. All who is active, curious, and playful while maintaining our inner beauty, strength, independence, and shrewd perception. 

My very first Open Edition piece. Sending out the positive vibe to all the Web3 friends who are still here through ups and downs. Let's keep our tiger spirit burning bright. We will thrive and make it wonderful!

5000 x 5000 px  
Digital Illustration
